scene.message:
Yukino: Hm? This is...{nl}
the Principal's office?{nl}
Why is it here??{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: Oishi, "Vice{nl}
Principal," you mean to say{nl}
my, the "Principal's,"{waitkey}{clearbox}teaching policy is wrong?{nl}
That's what you're saying,{nl}
"Vice Principal" Oishi?{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: No, Hannya,{nl}
"Principal," that's not it.{nl}
It's just that I...{waitkey}{clearbox}A rule where a student late{nl}
three times is expelled, or{nl}
shines "Principal" Hannya's{waitkey}{clearbox}shoes till graduation...{nl}
isn't that a bit much...?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: It seems we're in the{nl}
dream of the V.P. and{nl}
the Principal.{waitkey}{clearbox}V.P. Hannya has become{nl}
"Principal," and Principal{nl}
Oishi the "Vice Principal"...{waitkey}{clearbox}Most likely the Principal{nl}
got dragged into that vulgar{nl}
V.P.'s dream. Something so.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Huh huh huh?{nl}
V.P. Hannya's "Principal"?{nl}
Principal Oishi's "V.P."?{waitkey}{clearbox}What's going on?{nl}
Oh, I get it! This is{nl}
Hannya and Oishi's dream!{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: What did you say!{nl}
Oishi, "Vice Principal"!{nl}
A mere "V.P." like you,{waitkey}{clearbox}finding fault with the{nl}
splendid rule I, "Principal"{nl}
Hannya, thought up?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Right! New rule! Any teacher{nl}
who knocks the "Principal's"{nl}
rule is fired! Fired, fired!{waitkey}You're fired~!!{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi:{nl}
"Thought up"?!{nl}
Hannya, "Principal"!!{nl}
You decided the school rules{waitkey}on a whim?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Absurd. Truly absurd.{nl}
An exchange I can't bear{nl}
to listen to.{waitkey}{clearbox}Is this the conversation of{nl}
men who call themselves{nl}
educators?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: V.P. Hannya's "dream,"{nl}
so full of desire, must have{nl}
a very strong power.{waitkey}{clearbox}To drag even Principal Oishi{nl}
into his own dream...{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: Sh-shut up!{nl}
What's wrong with deciding{nl}
rules on a whim?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Call it what you will,{nl}
I'm the greatest at this{nl}
school! A god, you could say!{waitkey}{clearbox}My voice is the voice of god!{nl}
The will of the great cosmos!{nl}
Understand?!{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: Hannya,{nl}
"Principal"!! What do you{nl}
think education even is?{waitkey}{clearbox}To begin with...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Let's just wake them{nl}
up already. I really can't{nl}
stand listening.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Still, this is an{nl}
awfully realistic{nl}
Principal's office.{waitkey}{clearbox}If no one told you, you'd{nl}
never know it's a dream.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ahh,{nl}
let's get back to school.{nl}
Ayase's tired!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: We who go peering{nl}
through others' dreams have{nl}
no right to say it, but{waitkey}{clearbox}being shown such naked human{nl}
desire is not a pleasant{nl}
feeling.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Whoa~!{nl}
Wanna take a break on the{nl}
sofa set here?{waitkey}{clearbox}...Just kidding.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: For a dream world,{nl}
it's not such a Romantic{nl}
place, is it.{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: Later -{nl}
I must persuade the{nl}
"Principal."{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: Get lost,{nl}
now!! I'll have you{nl}
shining shoes!!{waitkey}{ret}
